<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19876</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您还不能叫陪审团裁决。” 白兔对国王解释说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22633</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有更多的证据。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>白兔弯下腰，捡起一张折着的纸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看到了吗？这是刚刚找到的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后想要仔细地看看。“是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我还没有打开。” 白兔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可能是武士写给某人的信。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要是没有收信人的话，” 国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58728</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那就更奇怪了。” 陪审员们同意地点点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63564</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“信是写给谁的？” 一名陪审员问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有写是给谁的。” 白兔打开纸说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73955</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“纸背面什么都没有写。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73955</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哦，这不是一封信，是一首诗。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87924</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是囚犯的笔迹吗？” 另一名陪审员问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87924</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是。真奇怪！” 白兔说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100837</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“武士肯定是模仿了其他人的笔迹。” 国王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100837</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104970</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>武士叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陛下，我没有写那首诗，没有人能证明是我写的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111245</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>诗最后有署名吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>白兔仔细地读了读诗，然后摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119308</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有，没有看到署名。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125933</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，国王还是不满意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134342</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他对武士说：“你没有署名，只会让事情变得更糟糕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很明显，你有什么不好的企图。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145351</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>否则，你会像一个诚实的人一样署名的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145351</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151694</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>法庭里的人都热烈地鼓起掌来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151694</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是国王今天说的第一句有道理的话！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155760</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一名陪审员对另一名陪审员说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“肃静！” 王后说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166862</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都安静了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果武士没有署名，这就证明他有罪，所以砍下……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不对！那什么都证明不了。” 爱丽丝说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你连诗的内容是什么都不知道。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把诗念一念！” 国王命令白兔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193959</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陛下，从哪里开始念呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193959</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从开头开始，” 国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一直大声念到最后。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202123</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>白兔照做了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204982</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210491</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他念诗的时候，整个法庭都很安静。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我听过的最荒唐的诗了。” 爱丽丝想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一点儿意义都没有。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王却有不同的想法。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我们今天听到的最重要的证据。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225357</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他搓了搓手，“现在陪审团必须作出……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果陪审团中有人可以解释清楚，我就给他钱。” 爱丽丝说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239920</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得那首诗没有任何意义。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她已经变得很大了，所以她并不害怕国王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王没理她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259805</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“陪审团，你们的裁决是什么？” 他这句话大约说了二十次。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259806</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263860</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是这样的！” 王后说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263860</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“先判刑，再问陪审团的意见。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268207</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272196</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“太不合理了！” 爱丽丝大声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272196</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275313</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有人先判刑的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275313</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果陪审团觉得武士没有罪呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那根本就不需要判刑！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>287354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“肃静！” 王后说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>287354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的脸气成了紫色。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290377</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293557</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不要！” 爱丽丝说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293557</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“砍掉她的头！” 王后大声喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>没有人动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307459</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁在乎你的想法？” 爱丽丝说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307459</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>312208</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，她已经变成了原来的大小。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>312208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>317184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们只不过是扑克牌而已！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>317184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329063</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>说完这话，扑克牌们飞了起来，扑向了爱丽丝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>